{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The Great Indian Bloggers&nbsp;Meet","content":"<p><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/\"><img data-attachment-id=\"743\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/feature/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2336,1301\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;11&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D3100&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421418639&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;3200&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"feature\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-743 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=390\" alt=\"feature\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=390 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=780 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=84 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=251 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/feature1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=428 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /></a></p>\n<h5>14<sup>th</sup> January</h5>\n<p>A friend asks me to go to Park Street for the &#8216;Bloggers&#8217; meet&#8217; on Friday.</p>\n<blockquote><p>When? And where?</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;padding-left:30px;\">2:30 [PM]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;padding-left:30px;\">Park Street</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;padding-left:30px;\">Oxford Book Store</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">I made it certain that I would attend the meet.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><!--more--></p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">For the first time in India, blogging was made a part of a literary fest.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;padding-left:30px;\"><a href=\"http://www.aklf.in/\">The Apeejay Kolkata Literary Festival (AKLF) 2015</a> was held from 14<sup>th</sup> to 18<sup>th</sup> January at various heritage sites in Kolkata. On the 16<sup>th</sup> of January, bloggers from all age groups gathered in the iconic Oxford Book Store, at Park Street, for the award distribution ceremony of the &#8216;Great Indian Blogging Contest&#8217;, and to hear from established bloggers speak about SEO, self branding, monetizing blogs, presenting creative blog posts, and much more.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;padding-left:30px;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"679\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/img_9443-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"5184,3456\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Soupayan Dutta&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 600D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421419304&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;400&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00625&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IMG_9443-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-679\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=660&#038;h=440\" alt=\"IMG_9443-2\" width=\"660\" height=\"440\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=660&amp;h=440 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=880 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=150&amp;h=100 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=450&amp;h=300 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=768&amp;h=512 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9443-2.jpg?w=700&amp;h=467 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">The event was organized with support from <a href=\"http://www.kolkatabloggers.com\">Kolkata Bloggers</a>. <a href=\"http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/\">The Times of India</a> (TOI) and <a href=\"http://www.oxfordbookstore.com/dotcom/oxford/\">Oxford Bookstore</a> were partners. There were six speakers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"#Jit\">Jit Sengupta</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"#Saha\">Anirban Saha</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"#Suman\">Suman Chakraborty</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"#Sen\">Shibnath Sen</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"#Aji\">Aji Isaac Mathew</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"#Shilpa\">Shilpa Srivastava</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also saw the <a href=\"#prizes\">prize distribution</a> later in the evening.</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">At 2:30 PM, I reached Oxford Bookstore,</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"678\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/img_9439-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"5020,3327\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Soupayan Dutta&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 600D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421419188&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;400&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.00625&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IMG_9439-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=700\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-678\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=660&#038;h=437\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=660&amp;h=437 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=874 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=450&amp;h=298 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=768&amp;h=509 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9439-11.jpg?w=700&amp;h=464 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">and climbed up to the first floor. One part of the first floor contains the &#8216;<a href=\"http://www.oxfordbookstore.com/dotcom/oxford/discover/cha_bar/index.htm\">Cha Bar</a>&#8216; &#8211; a small food corner. The other portion had been made ready for the event.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_733\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"733\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/sitting/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2336,1111\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;3.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D3100&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421419088&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;18&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"sitting\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-733\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=660&#038;h=314\" alt=\"The bloggers meet\" width=\"660\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=660&amp;h=314 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=628 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=150&amp;h=71 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=450&amp;h=214 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=768&amp;h=365 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sitting.jpg?w=700&amp;h=333 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">The bloggers meet</figcaption></figure>\n<p id=\"Jit\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"https://in.linkedin.com/pub/jit-sengupta/27/3a0/92\">Jit Sengupta</a>, the Assistant Brand Manager of East Zone at TOI would be conducting the whole event.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_728\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"728\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/jit/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2336,1542\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D3100&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421420997&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;98&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.016666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-728\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=660&#038;h=436\" alt=\"Jit Sengupta (when he was reading out the prize winners)\" width=\"660\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=660&amp;h=436 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=872 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=450&amp;h=297 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=768&amp;h=507 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/jit.jpg?w=700&amp;h=462 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jit Sengupta (when he was reading out the prize winners) [Photograph by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayanphotography123?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts\">Sayan Biswas</a>]</figcaption></figure>\n<p id=\"Saha\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"http://www.anirbansaha.com/\">Anirban Saha</a>, the founder of Kolkata Bloggers was the first speaker. He presented us the advantages of blogging with examples from his own life &#8211; how blogging escalated his confidence as a speaker and improved his English as well. He told us how blogging provides a competitive advantage to everyone, especially to aspiring authors.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">When you have your work discoverable online, you open an entire range of opportunities for yourself</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_682\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"682\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/img_9474-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"4761,3144\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Soupayan Dutta&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 600D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421420890&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;37&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IMG_9474-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-682 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=462\" alt=\"IMG_9474-1\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=462 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=924 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=297 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9474-1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=507 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anirban Saha</figcaption></figure>\n<p>The world now lives and breathes online. Two terms were introduced &#8211; <strong>branding </strong>and <strong>promotion</strong>. Suppose you are going to introduce yourself to someone for the first time. Basically, the latter does the job beforehand. He &#8216;Googles&#8217; you. He researches you. Now consider this:</p>\n<blockquote><p>What if you can not impress him? He might not meet you and you might lose an opportunity.</p>\n<p>Your visibility and interactions online, creates a small brand for yourself.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Before leaving the dias, he gave us examples of how some bloggers made an offline presence with their content &#8211; The Great Bong, Arnab Ray, Anuradha Goyal, Suchi Singh Kalra.</p>\n<div id=\"Suman\">\n<p>Following him, <a href=\"http://yourstory.com/2011/06/suman-chakraborty-roman-books-literary-fiction-and-poetry-for-general-trade/\">Suman Chakraborty</a>, CEO and executive editor of <a href=\"http://www.romanbooks.co.in/\">Roman Books</a>, utilized a PowerPoint presentation to give us a brief idea about what publishers look for in writers. Along with that he informed us about a new project they would be undertaking &#8211; Roman Books would be picking out certain blog posts from various interested Indian bloggers and collating them into a book. The idea had stemmed from a senior editor at Roman Books &#8211; who had a blog that addressed letters to various day-to-day elements.</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_684\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"684\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/img_9508-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"5184,2630\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5.6&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Soupayan Dutta&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 600D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421422559&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;55&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.033333333333333&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IMG_9508-1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Suman Chakraborty&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-684 size-large\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=355\" alt=\"IMG_9508-1\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=700&amp;h=355 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;h=710 1400w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=76 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=228 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9508-1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=390 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Suman Chakraborty</figcaption></figure>\n<p>He notified us of the various elements Roman Books would be looking for in a blog post, emphasizing on <strong>creativity </strong>and <strong>saleability</strong>, lastly mentioning that only fairly established blogs, with good reviews and comments would be considered for the book.</p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"Sen\">\n<p>Shib Nath Sen of <a href=\"https://www.jwt.com/india\">JWT</a>, an advertising agency, followed Mr. Chakraborty, with how to use blogs as a boost to sales and presence. He uses his blog to vent out the pressure from his career.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Blogs must touch the reader&#8217;s heart and everyone needs to develop a style of his own</p></blockquote>\n<p>He gave a few examples of how a distinctive style sets apart companies. Apple simply makes things differently. They have good marketing skills.</p>\n<blockquote><p>We just happen to make great computers &#8211; Apple</p></blockquote>\n<p>He also narrated incidents from his life to explain proper presentation that should be done in blog posts.</p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"Aji\">\n<p><a href=\"http://aji.techshu.com/\">Aji Isaac Mathew</a>, CEO of <a href=\"http://www.techshu.com/\">Techshu</a> was next. His presentation would primarily concern the topic &#8216;<strong>How Easy is SEO?</strong>&#8216;</p>\n<p><figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_721\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"721\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/aji/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1351\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"aji\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-721\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=700&#038;h=461\" alt=\"Aji Isaac Mathew\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=700&amp;h=461 700w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=1398&amp;h=922 1398w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=450&amp;h=297 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/aji.jpg?w=768&amp;h=507 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aji Isaac Mathew [Photograph by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayanphotography123?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts\">Sayan Biswas</a>]</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<p>He touched some extremely valid points about blogging in general. Each and every blogger should have a target audience. Humans around the world have common interests. A person blogging for a particular reason might provide valid information for another person.</p>\n<blockquote><p>The reason why you are blogging is the reason why others will read it</p></blockquote>\n<p>SEO stands for <strong>S</strong>earch <strong>E</strong>ngine <strong>O</strong>ptimization. Aji introduced a valid point:</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:30px;\">SEO is a backdated concept. Blogs, nowadays, should target SMO &#8211; <strong>S</strong>earch <strong>M</strong>edia <strong>O</strong>ptimization.</p>\n<p>Earlier, he used various RSS readers, such as Google Reader to get updates from various blogs. Now, the scenario has changed.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Nowadays, you don&#8217;t reach out to blogs. Blogs come to you.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"padding-left:30px;\"><strong>Everyone</strong>, around the globe, shares on various social networks. Thus, getting updates from bloggers is no longer something the reader needs to concern himself with.</p>\n<p>Initially, monetizing a blog should not be the blogger&#8217;s goal. He should write for passion. Later, when the blogger starts to get traffic, proper archiving should be done. For many, a blog is a form of catharsis. However, it should be kept in mind, blog posts can have long term effects if done properly. &#8216;The perfect blog post&#8217; is not easy. And no such thing exists. You can only strive to do better.</p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"Shilpa\">\n<p>Before Anirban Saha went up on the dias again, the last speaker Shilpa Srivastava, Social Media Lead of <a href=\"http://www.infobase.co.in/\">Compare Infobase</a>, provided insights on how to promote blogs. She constantly emphasized on leaving behind the &#8216;first person factor&#8217;.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Come out of the &#8216;I&#8217; factor. Your blog should be more popular than you and not the other way around.</p></blockquote>\n<p>A wonderful piece of advice got hard-coded into my mind. Bloggers should initially &#8216;release teasers&#8217; of their upcoming blog post. These teasers should be shared on various social media platforms. She included something she had done herself. Before releasing a post on a recent vintage car rally race, she had posted:</p>\n<blockquote><p>Do you know the difference between &#8216;vintage cars&#8217; and &#8216;classic cars&#8217;?</p></blockquote>\n<p>This was something many were unaware of.</p>\n<p>She advised that bloggers should maintain a profile on <a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/\">Pinterest</a>, apart from <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\">Facebook</a>,<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/\"> Google+ </a>and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/\">Twitter</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<div id=\"prizes\">\n<p>During the event, prizes were handed out to the winners of the &#8216;Great Indian Blogging Contest&#8217;. 70+ valid entries had come from members of the Kolkata Bloggers team itself. The topic announced by TOI had been</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left:30px;\">&#8216;The Great Indian Chamcha&#8217; &#8211; a humorous take on the culture of sycophancy that runs deep in politics and has slowly become part of our daily lives.</p>\n<p>Actor-author Tisca Chopra gave away the prizes to the top three blogs posts &#8211; Namrata Kumari, Rushati Mukherjee and Sohaiil Mohammed (mentioned according to their ranks). Amartya Talukdar won the award for the most engaging blog.</p>\n<p><figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_729\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"729\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/second/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2336,1542\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D3100&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421421074&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;62&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.02&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"second\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-729\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=660&#038;h=436\" alt=\"Rushati Mukherjee\" width=\"660\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=660&amp;h=436 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=872 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=450&amp;h=297 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=768&amp;h=507 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/second.jpg?w=700&amp;h=462 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rushati Mukherjee [Photograph by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayanphotography123?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts\">Sayan Biswas</a>]</figcaption></figure><figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_730\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"730\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/sohaiil/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2336,1542\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.2&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D3100&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421421033&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;62&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"sohaiil\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-730\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=660&#038;h=436\" alt=\"Sohaiil Mohammed\" width=\"660\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=660&amp;h=436 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=872 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=150&amp;h=99 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=450&amp;h=297 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=768&amp;h=507 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/sohaiil.jpg?w=700&amp;h=462 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sohaiil Mohammed [Photograph by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayanphotography123?ref=ts&amp;fref=ts\">Sayan Biswas</a>]</figcaption></figure></p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_705\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"705\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/img_9497-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"4675,2728\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Soupayan Dutta&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 600D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1421421501&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;29&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;1600&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.033333333333333&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IMG_9497-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=700\" class=\"wp-image-705\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=660&#038;h=385\" alt=\"Amartya Talukdar - receiving the 'most engaging blog' award\" width=\"660\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=660&amp;h=385 660w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=1320&amp;h=770 1320w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=150&amp;h=88 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=450&amp;h=263 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=768&amp;h=448 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/img_9497-12.jpg?w=700&amp;h=408 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Amartya Talukdar &#8211; receiving the &#8216;most engaging blog&#8217; award</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<p>The event was of-its-own-kind. The points enumerated by Anirban Saha, Aji Isaac Mathew, Shilpa Srivastava and Shib Nath Sen were valuable. I believe these are necessities for <strong>every </strong>blogger, irrespective of where they are living, or which society they come from, or even their age group. This was a big event for Kolkata Bloggers.</p>\n<p>As a young blogger who has just started to share his work, this was very knowledgeable. Tips about sharing with &#8216;pre-teasers&#8217;, concept of SMO, branding and promotion are certain things I will keep in mind in my future posts. Teasers are something I will certainly use in the future, for example, when I&#8217;m writing about travelling to a certain place.</p>\n<p>I congratulate the winners of the &#8216;Great Indian Blogging Contest&#8217;. From the little snippets Jit Sengupta read out (from their respective posts), I felt that TOI had made proper judgement.</p>\n<p>The following day, that is one the 17<sup>th</sup> of January, TOI included the bloggers meet:</p>\n<figure data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_731\" style=\"width: 710px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"731\" data-permalink=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.wordpress.com/2015/01/18/the-great-indian-bloggers-meet/newspaper/\" data-orig-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1257,513\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"newspaper\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=450\" data-large-file=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-731\" src=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=700&#038;h=285\" alt=\"Newspaper clipping from TOI [dated 17th of January, 2015]\" srcset=\"https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=698&amp;h=285 698w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=61 150w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=450&amp;h=184 450w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=313 768w, https://nabhoneelparchments.files.wordpress.com/2015/01/newspaper1.jpg 1257w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"   /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Newspaper clipping from TOI [dated 17<sup>th</sup> of January, 2015]</figcaption></figure>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">All photographs (except for the ones mentioned) were shot by Soupayan Dutta at the event. Check out his photography page on Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/soupayanduttaphotography?fref=ts\">Soupayan Dutta Photography</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:'Courier New';\">I obtained certain quotes from the event from the article in Times of India: <a href=\"http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/Want-to-be-a-blogger-Experts-tell-you-how/articleshow/45916493.cms\">Want to be a blogger? Experts tell you how</a></span></p>\n","date":"2015-01-17T19:50:02.000Z","slug":"the-great-indian-bloggers-meet","excerpt":"<p>I believe these are necessities for every blogger, irrespective of where they are living, or which society they come from, or even their age group.</p>\n"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nabhoneel's Parchments","subtitle":"All thing photographed and written down"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"89918b3c-4ab4-50c1-9f3d-49a8b073b885"}}